824,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"9b8ff75c48b80eb9cbbefe1aec6767204d2e79fb","tid":661824,"uid":33939,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"239f5d7183aaaf902639ce39b5db6f034baa1e9e","tid":661824,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"構圖同光，色呢啲後制都得。如果你有心我就教你啦。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"不了，要返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"你追下我啲post都大把野學到。"},{"pid":"df6ecab1a92919875967676549beb7fd0dc96f6a","tid":661824,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cab05509616eea7a8a957b4ed5e47c47c90d0c7","tid":661824,"uid":122208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"John Berger 既Way of seeing"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"係 不過我真係頂唔順 真係好悶<br />\n如果樓主有興趣睇理論可以睇呢本 好出名"},{"pid":"3c64e6a68258b6e8d07ce278590cdc5740604943","tid":661824,"uid":4706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"John Berger唔止ways of seeing<br />\n仲有觀看的視界<br />\n攝影的異義等等<br />\n<br />\nSusan Sontag一堆<br />\n論攝影<br />\n旁觀他人之痛苦<br />\n<br />\n有本叫這就是當代攝影都好好<br />\n（譯得有d難睇但講既野好好的）<br />\n<br />\n可以睇埋台灣攝影之聲雜誌<br />\n成日會搵到好多好勁既artist訪問"},{"pid":"2bcedd20f7488207e226e4e19792e08ac1de69d9","tid":661824,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:58:45.000Z","msg":"thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75502ad9b4554b3b9e578f451341a4c6e5bd0558","tid":661824,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/212128_de4dfccc9b6e18a27d6cf5e6765f0210.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F212128_de4dfccc9b6e18a27d6cf5e6765f0210.png&h=2e963a52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a0881f5857b319690d8812537c594315c65b624","tid":661824,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T13:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/212400_a697195f82940a92f2d5a344088b38e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F212400_a697195f82940a92f2d5a344088b38e9.png&h=f16da403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伍振榮 榮榮"},{"pid":"bf8227f6617d09760c98caf4cf9f8b8556d14a3f","tid":661824,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df6ecab1a92919875967676549beb7fd0dc96f6a","tid":661824,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cab05509616eea7a8a957b4ed5e47c47c90d0c7","tid":661824,"uid":122208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"John Berger 既Way of seeing"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"係 不過我真係頂唔順 真係好悶<br />\n如果樓主有興趣睇理論可以睇呢本 好出名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T18:03:29.000Z","msg":"之前剛剛睇完<br />\n作為理科仔<br />\n入面用嘅language對我黎講需要更長時間理解<br />\n<br />\n本書講攝影的部份唔多<br />\n甚至對相機的出現有所保留<br />\n節錄部份內文:<br />\n&quot;The camera isolated momentary appearances and <br />\nin so doing<strong><em>destroyed the idea that images were timeless</em></strong>. <br />\nOr, to put it another way, the camera showed that<br />\n<strong><em>the notion of time passing was inseparable from the experience of the visual</em></strong> (except in paintings). &quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The uniqueness of every painting was once part of the uniqueness of the place where it resided. <br />\nSometimes the painting was transportable. <br />\nBut it could never be seen in two places at the same time. <br />\nWhen the camera reproduces a painting, <br />\nit <strong><em>destroys the uniqueness of its image</em></strong>. <br />\nAs a result its meaning changes.<br />\nOr, more exactly, its meaning multiplies and fragments into many meanings&quot;<br />\n<br />\n除咗攝影<br />\n本書反而更著墨於畫作嘅分析、含意，以至與社會嘅互動<br />\n例如裸體畫的特色、裸體畫如何反映兩性間嘅地位差異<br />\n對畫作成為富人炫耀財富嘅批判<br />\n亦係未段帶出廣告硬照透過模仿或借用古典畫作<br />\n去推使大眾追求奢華的生活方式<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢話呢本書可以令你對攝影有更深認識<br />\n但起碼使你知道畫作或照片內嘅 details 可以包含唔少嘅意義<br />\n最後，分享多一段較深刻嘅內容<br />\n<br />\n&quot;If the new language of images were used differently, <br />\nit would, through its use, confer a new kind of power. <br />\nWithin it we could begin to define our experiences more precisely in areas <br />\nwhere words are inadequate. (Seeing comes before words.) <br />\nNot only personal experience, <br />\nbut also the essential historical experience of our relation to the past: <br />\nthat is to say the experience of seeking to give meaning to our lives,<br />\nof trying to understand the history of which we can become the active agents.&quot;"},{"pid":"b0ecb3573fdca7b64757cd7098722313d21da765","tid":661824,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"我會更推介 John Berger 的另一本著作 Understanding a Photograph<br />\n亦有講 Eugene Smith, Henri Cartier-Bresson 同 Salgado"},{"pid":"b27fe51b0fb037c16bb9cca74240149e01c6d735","tid":661824,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T18:21:48.000Z","msg":"頭兩條片係 Bruce Gilden 評相<br />\n佢對相嘅評價好值得去深思<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jNilCJTcJxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjNilCJTcJxA&d=U8lfYkp3pziho3dMdODr2pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c6a253ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jNilCJTcJxA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/540JpC9IbEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F540JpC9IbEU&d=U8lfYkp3pziho3dMdODr2pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2394c0c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/540JpC9IbEU</a><br />\n<br />\n另外係記錄Garry Winogrand 攝影嘅心態<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3RM9KcYEYXs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3RM9KcYEYXs&d=U8lfYkp3pziho3dMdODr2pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=89525dc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3RM9KcYEYXs</a>"},{"pid":"54852ee09b148f99e4d199454ad74fa93b05543b","tid":661824,"uid":122208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df6ecab1a92919875967676549beb7fd0dc96f6a","tid":661824,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cab05509616eea7a8a957b4ed5e47c47c90d0c7","tid":661824,"uid":122208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"John Berger 既Way of seeing"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"係 不過我真係頂唔順 真係好悶<br />\n如果樓主有興趣睇理論可以睇呢本 好出名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:27:21.000Z","msg":"係悶既，當年讀design要讀喱本野"}]}